data.description: Located in the quaint town of West Point, within ten minutes of I-64 great location for commuters to Richmond, Williamsburg and Newport news. This adorable one level rancher offers, three bedrooms, two full baths, one car garage, and a large private deck on the back.  Newly remodeled kitchen in 2022 with stainless steel appliances, pantry and plenty of cabinetry. Hardwood floor throughout the house and beautiful wood fireplace in the family room. This house offers the following updates: New roof in 2021, updated kitchen in 2022, Tankless water heater 2020, updated guest bathroom 2022, new gutter, new roof on back deck, new storm door, new blinds and new garage door. The garage was Re-insulted in 2023. This home is one block from the Lewis B Puller Beach access a few minutes to WEST POINT Glass Island Public boat ramp, fishing pier and walking distance to the river.
